            java.lang.String name,

            int minutes,

            java.lang.String genre)
        Constructor of the song class.
        pre: parameters are initialized.
        post: Song class object created.
        Parameters:
        tittle - Song tittle. tittle != "". tittle != null.
        name - artist song name. name != "". name != null.
        date - Release date of the song. date != "". date != null.
        minutes - Duration minutes of the song. minutes bigger or equals than 0
        seconds - Duration seconds of the song. seconds bigger than 0
        genre - Genre of the song. The genre has to be an existing genre in the Category enum
